# dukatools

Cross-platform CLI toolbelt.

## Install
uv tool install dukatools

## Upgrade
uv tool upgrade dukatools

## Commands
- treex — enhanced directory tree
- dirproc — directory batch processor

## Usage
treex --help
dirproc --help

